            "brand_sub_heading": "<h2>[* <strong>Heart diseases</strong>*]</h2>",
            "content_1": "<p>Research in USA on men aged between 71 and 93 showed for each mile they walked each day they reduced the risk of heart disease by 30%. So 6 minutes exercise on a Rebounder per day should greatly reduce risk of heart disease. Excellent for increasing your heartbeat on a regular basis.</p>",
            "image_conetnt_block_content_1": "<h2></h2><h2>[*<strong>Cycling, Running & Rowing Machines</strong>*]</h2><p>How long did you keep it up on such expensive machines? Got bored? A Rebounder is much cheaper, so you can have one at home for the whole family to enjoy – a far more efficient and quicker way to exercise the whole body.</p>",
            "content_2": "<h2></h2><h2>[* <strong>Right Equipment</strong>*]</h2><p>Even fit people can end up with aches and pains from using the wrong equipment. The PT Rebounder is the only Rebounder recommended by BBC Watchdog Health check and AFTA. Built to professional specification and is the very best <a href=\"https://www.dulwichhealth.co.uk/product/pt-rebounder-uk-only/?v=13b5bfe96f3e\"><strong>Rebounder</strong></a> available. The PT Rebounder is not springy. It has a firm self-centering mat, which will give you a feeling of security. With 9″ legs the PT Rebounder will stand on its side, when not in use and its special rubber feet protect your carpet.</p><p></p><p>Support Bar (extra) provides support and confidence for the injured, the infirm, the elderly and the handicapped. Also useful for people with impaired sight.</p>",
            "image_conetnt_block_content_2": "<h2></h2><h2>[* <strong>Body Mass Index (BMI)</strong>*]</h2><p>To find your right weight for your height you need to measure your BMI, 19 to 25 is normal, 25 to 30 is overweight, 30 and over is obese. Under 18 is too thin.</p><p></p><p>If you want to loose weight don’t make the mistake of drastically cutting calories over long periods. Within 3 hours your body will be in ‘starvation mode’ and your body will start storing fat.</p>",
